      <heading>Sun Jan 23 (Kazin)      :: Cool Sayings</heading>
      <slot>1</slot>
      <level>21</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>Just a bunch of really cool CotL sayings I picked up and
adapted from a variety of sources, something to spice
up your rants..... I mean speaches.

-Darkfriends commit two crimes.  The first is turning from
the path of the Light, and the second is the embrace the Darkness
through which they tread.  For the first, they may be forgiven,
if they return to Walk in the Light.  For the second, there
is only death.

-Your honor is your life, let none despute it.

-An empty mind is like unto freshly turned sod.  If not sown
with the seeds of love, duty, and honor, the insidious
weeds of heresy take root.

-Darkfriends have only one purpose and there is nothing they
will not do to accomplish this, no matter how vile or loath-
some it might be.  These abominations mean to destroy
everything proud and noble, everything we hold dear and
have fought so long to achieve.

-Thought begets Heresty, Heresy begets Retribution.

-The Dark One has many forms.  You must know them all.  You must
tell the Dark One from his disguise and root him from the hidden
places.  Trust no one.  Trust not even yourself.  It is better
to die in vain than to live in abomination.  The zealous martyr
is praised for his valor, the craven and the unready are justly
abhorred.

There's a sample, if anyone wants more, mail me or post here.
-Kazin's player.
</text>
