      <heading>Tue Jun  4 (Angua)      :: &amp;wNew Gskill, And Rules Of Use&amp;n</heading>
      <slot>26</slot>
      <level>203</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>&amp;wDisguise.

This skill will be given to the guild spies/assains only. So they will be able to disguise their names for roleplay only. The skill is also given on a trust basis that it will be used properly and for IC purposes. 

here are a few rules to follow.

1. disguise must be only used in an IC manner. Using disguise to make up non IC names ,bookies names and any other popular character from tv, books ect. will not be tollerated.


2. No dramatic changes to a Guildies descrition. eg. You cannot make yourself thinner. you cannot change your eye color and so forth. Weight cannot be changed.Height cannot be changed and neither can one's eye color. Scars birth marks and so forth may be disguise by the use of makeup, that is if your character knows how to do that.

3. There are certain races that you cannot disguise to be.
Such are as follows:

Aiel
Seachan
Seafolk
Ogier.

Any Breaking of these rules will result in punishment. So please use the skill in a logical manner.

Angua.
</text>
